{"tid":1800720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(遊行集人)一定要做好連儂牆，人傳人宣傳","createTime":"2019-12-28T05:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T11:48:57.000Z","uid":78222,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"07fd7ca7ce22beb1b28f35449ab74d45e8dc2f3d","tid":1800720,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"宣傳分三部份，之前大家都做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫大家總結小小<br />\n實體版，電子版，現實人傳人版<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個人認為實體版非常重要！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為太多人唔擅長用互聯網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>1.實體文宣</ins></span></span><br />\n✓光復連儂牆<br />\n✓地下痴返(11)以示元旦大遊行<br />\n✓派傳單(我覺得最有用但最費成本)<br />\n✓周圍痴貼街招<br />\n✓連儂廁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">近排都有狗捉鳩人痴文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴文宣前要組團，提高警覺，小心被跟</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>2.電子版文宣</ins></span></span><br />\n✓地鐵/出街Airdrop<br />\n✓WhatsApp<span style=\"color: orange;\">銀髮message</span><br />\n打曬活動時間日期地址<br />\n(for<span style=\"color: orange;\">精靈銀髮一族</span>, 銀髮group互傳用)<br />\n✓長輩圖<span style=\"color: red;\">(for藍絲廢老</span>)<br />\n✓fb / ig share<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>3.現實人傳人版</ins></span></span><br />\n✓同自己身邊嘅人講<br />\n✓同親戚食飯記得講1月1有遊行<br />\n✓和理非可以同朋友組團參與<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A142epb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA142epb.png&h=1cf0ca6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NvKtUpc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvKtUpc.jpg&h=3b7daefe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrW0LvT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrW0LvT.png&h=9b98adf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CSFQohA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCSFQohA.png&h=e5b59b95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"102ca5d8d189baa9e33444c07540ba458cde9891","tid":1800720,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:45:50.000Z","msg":"（聯署）你班友快Ｄ同我簽晒佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799015</a>"},{"pid":"aa7a98bbd31e569d0b1c0fac2526d92c89327c76","tid":1800720,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"毋忘承諾，並肩同行<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n日期：2020年1月1日 （三）<br />\n時間：14:00<br />\n路線：維園中央草坪 至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\n🌟不反對通知書申請中"},{"pid":"03f76778c0fd7ec6a7650568edaf0653e9af1293","tid":1800720,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"記住用連儂牆去做宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f139a2e63c22fbb40d54f6d33736e1043a922a03","tid":1800720,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"推連登post係有用<br />\n但最重要係將訊息帶俾無上連登嘅人呀"},{"pid":"a24ae916881692932b4090da5b7b25ba43048957","tid":1800720,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:51:16.000Z","msg":"現實世界要出盡力宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800386</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"38a4359b45350d9b8c88e25bf20c2d9e216365a3","tid":1800720,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:52:4